Package: nrsaDemo
Title: NRSA Field Data Review Application
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Oklahoma Water Resources Board", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "owrb@owrb.ok.gov")
Description: A Shiny application for reviewing and summarising National Rivers
    and Streams Assessment (NRSA) habitat field data. Supports data loading via
    Excel file upload or a direct ODBC connection to an AWQMS database, with
    interactive summary tables, transect-completeness checks, and a Leaflet site
    map.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
